The paper proposes a new image captioning architecture using tensor product representations (TPR), which is a structured neural-symbolic framework developed in cognitive science. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also integrates deep learning (DL) with explicit language structures and rules, indicating that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
